        <Summary>Advanced Diff tool</Summary>
        <Description>kdiff3-kde4 is a file and directory diff and merge tool which compares and merges two or three text input files or directories. It shows the differences line by line and character by character(!), provides an automatic merge-facility and has an editor for comfortable solving of merge-conflicts.</Description>
